{"id": 1739, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得如今这些“科技感”的非必要元素是啥？", "description": "科技感最重要的难道不是技术本人吗？技术都没有就捣腾这些“科技感花哨元素”，现在宣称是黑科技的产品都在用什么搏眼球！啊！", "record_count": 11647, "comment_count": 28, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201706131811131xjYdQaFXUArpcCD.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-14T17:00:48Z", "questions": [{"id": 2447, "title": "你觉得如今这些“科技感”的非必要元素是啥？", "content": "你觉得“科技感”的非必要元素是啥？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 212642, "content": "产品名字里一定要有个带金字偏旁的字", "image": "img/option/option/20170614093046qVAyWik5wXl2ZUr9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 212643, "content": "PPT也要强调有科技感，背景深灰色，字体极简", "image": "img/option/option/20170614095405FTCh69X5P71mdliK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 212644, "content": "广告无限接近苹果风", "image": "img/option/option/20170614093128wqVX6Yahi2ncAvxf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 212645, "content": "品牌和产品logo主要是几何图形堆砌", "image": "img/option/option/20170614094452YD4OlHB1QURGwb2e.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 212646, "content": "模式起码搞三种以上，比如电动牙刷的“敏感/强劲/净白”", "image": "img/option/option/20170614094636RvS5LNEunTaxM6X2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 212647, "content": "颜色要金属色，不是金就是银，现在主要拼命跟风出玫瑰金", "image": "img/option/option/20170614093033HIhtiGpjYQuaRNlV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 212648, "content": "宣传用语里要有物理词汇，负离子等离子银离子啥的", "image": "img/option/option/20170614094923ZazfoQYbFS05Ap6t.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}